original: Hyltenius, Henry Johan Ragnar, kyrkoherde, Rydsnäs, f. 19/12/04 i Mellby, Jönköp. 1. — Stud:ex. i Eksjö 24, teol. fil. ex. 27, teol. kand., prakt, teol prov samt prästv. f. Lin-köp. stift 31. Pastorsadj. o. v. kom-min. i Vimmerby, v. pastor i Torpa, v. kommin. i Svinhult, kyrkoh. i Västra Ryd o. Svinhult 45.
translated: Hyltenius, Henry Johan Ragnar, parish priest, Rydsnäs, born December 19, 1904 in Mellby, Jönköping county. He graduated from high school in Eksjö in 1924, graduated with a Bachelor of Theology in 1927, completed practical theological training, passed the theological examination, and was ordained as a priest in the Linköping diocese in 1931. He worked as a pastor's assistant and deputy pastor in Vimmerby, deputy pastor in Torpa, deputy pastor in Svinhult, and was appointed as a parish priest in Västra Ryd and Svinhult in 1945.. He married in the year 19xx, but the partner's name was not provided.
